>   From the /lang/caml-light/Usercontribs, in ftp.inria.fr,
> I found 'caml-mode-0.72.*', and saw enclosed this file:
> 'camldebug.el'.  Do you know where to locate such 'camldebug'
> program?
> Using Object Caml v1.02, PC/linux.

The Caml debugger "camldebug" is currently available only for Caml
Light, and can be found in the Caml Light distribution. Some work has
been done on porting the debugger to Objective Caml, but it's not
finished yet.

- Xavier Leroy




